name: Projects by Gil M. Wilson, Jr.
body:
##Welcome!

This site will serve as a general index for work I will be doing throughout the next few months.  I'll have data analysis projects, as well as programming demos that will incorporate the use of:
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Java
- Python
- Markdown

and hopefully much, much more.  Feel free to check back periodically to see what's new!
